title: Royal Navy officer, 25, accused of raping woman while she slept is cleared by a jury in just 30 minutes
text:
Opinion 'RAPE' SAILOR CLEARED Royal Navy officer, 25, accused of raping woman while she slept is cleared by a jury in just 30 minutes 
Callum Fennell, 25, had earlier cried in the dock while telling the jury that he believed the woman had consented to sex in bed BY GEMMA MULLIN
